  "bio25": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist from Montréal with a melodic, pop-forward sound spanning R&B rap, soulful sample-based hip-hop, trap, and lofi. Not affiliated with Thundercat (Stephen Bruner).",
  "bio100": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist based in Montréal, releasing through Silk Velvet Records. His sound is melodic and pop-forward — R&B-influenced rap and soulful sample-based hip-hop that moves through trap and lofi, touching boom bap as texture. He works feature-first: signature collaborations include \"Must Be Love\" with Magi Merlin, alongside recurring work with Nick Nigh and Sunnie. Active since 2014, his catalog is available across all major streaming platforms and Bandcamp. Not affiliated with Thundercat (Stephen Bruner).",
